{"tid":1914973,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國不演了！發布192頁報告稱中國「不遵守WTO規範」","createTime":"2020-03-08T01:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T03:35:22.000Z","uid":141151,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6e84f140315f4fdf42d7bff34c9d7e266740686c","tid":1914973,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:15:52.000Z","msg":"美國不演了！發布192頁報告稱中國「不遵守WTO規範」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=703039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D703039&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=fbd08d38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D703039&h=c4ac62e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=703039</a><br />\n<br />\n稍早，美國貿易代表署發布了一份多達192頁的 報告，主要內容為評估2019年中國當局對於世界貿易組織（WTO）承諾的履行狀況，提及中方對「遵守WTO規範」一事仍然表現很差，且不只是不符其他會員國的預期，甚至與當時訂定的履約內容相差甚遠。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">美國貿易代表署在該份上交至國會的重要年度報告中可說是「火力全開」，指稱中國雖然承諾經濟改革，但實則仍以國家主導整個經濟體，使其他WTO的會員國承受了一定程度損失。再加上中國其獨裁政體的關係，時常以封閉的手段阻止外國的競爭，或是出手干預。<br />\n<br />\n另外，該份報告中的第125頁，對於新疆「再教育營」一事有不少的著墨。其內容敘述中國於新疆省有超過500個非自願拘留中心、監獄及教育營。當局針對包括維吾爾人在內超過100萬人實施強迫勞動、強行拘留及監禁，50頁則是提及當局封鎖了超過1萬個網站。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n先前，美國聯邦調查局（FBI）局長瑞伊（Christopher Wray）於參議院司法委員會聽證會上指稱「中國試圖偷竊美國的智慧財產權來取得經濟上的優勢」，並以美國當局的一千多件智慧財產權竊案近乎來自中國作為佐證。<br />\n<br />\n不料中國外交部發言人華春瑩「一不偷，二不搶，三不撒謊」作為回應，讓眾多網友不以為然。如今美國貿易代表署的192頁報告指出中國對於WTO的承諾及規範棄之不顧及壓迫人權的種種行徑，無非是重重打臉中方所述。"},{"pid":"3c3a1510489efd863bbc998aaa1ef6657ec48a8c","tid":1914973,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"wow"},{"pid":"95ca91171e1b8af973a011098ddff88c0afce4d4","tid":1914973,"uid":284228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:20:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5acc0a79997ec782a3ff46ede3ba418d7de0d77d","tid":1914973,"uid":42153,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:23:00.000Z","msg":"一不偷，二不搶，三不撒謊，四不信共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc79edb54b05cdbd9f32e77225644b7c32dfbc01","tid":1914973,"uid":247247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:26:01.000Z","msg":"This way sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfb0638264f512ad5f2ac9d54c0d4f701d28c19","tid":1914973,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecf413a9fdb3b898b7f91311c50c61efc932a50","tid":1914973,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:29:38.000Z","msg":"借位 大家幫手推一推<br />\n［行動post入黎推一推］ 明天1930將軍澳*準時到*<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1914250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1914250</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7c5a14a7beb96393ff16d18e786dd64a62c0748c","tid":1914973,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:59:16.000Z","msg":"寫埋香港落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c02d415078101db7968310649a970c3c16c75e7","tid":1914973,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T01:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce3fbcebd5dbf4c2f0c48027cd9521cc15e40b2","tid":1914973,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:00:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebc340801f0e1de327bb8a77f02173415944a03e","tid":1914973,"uid":281263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啲天滅中共"},{"pid":"ad2cf4c7928648a14ce35627661d6c1267433657","t